                                    <p>We provide Jaxx without charge. Our ability to do that depends partly on your taking responsibility for how you use Jaxx. The following three items are therefore fundamental to our agreement:
                                    <p>First, we can’t recover your Backup Phrase. We have no access to it. If you don’t install the Backup Phrase on a second device, write it down, and keep it in a safe place, you may lose access to your Digital Assets forever. Don’t do that.
